@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ogznft(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.sin((0.69 + (v0 + 0.29 / tmp + 0.47)))
    v2 = v0
    v2 = 0.72
    v0 = tmp
    v0 = wp.sin((wp.cos(tmp + 0.27) - (v1 + 0.46 * v1 + 0.74)))
    data[tid] = v0
